lines.text:
ROBIN HOOD, AND HIS GIANT
                LIEUTENANT,

LITTLEJOHN, GRIMLY STUDY THE
                CASTLE FROM

AT THE EDGE OF THE CLEARING,
                ROBIN STOPS

SUDDENLY, POINTS AHEAD...AND
                IN THE SHADOWS

IS OUTLINED THE FORM OF A
                STAG...

THE NEXT SECOND THEY ARE
                GASPING INTO THE
